00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:57.000
I can't make out anything from it.

00:02:58.679 --> 00:03:01.320
Is there someone named Qin Yu in the dream?

00:03:02.559 --> 00:03:03.279
Do you know him?

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:04.800
I'm not sure.

